title: Scrapbook (Switzerland), ca. 1900
description: 150 examples of woven silk plaid pinned and pasted into a scrapbook. Some, probably all, of the fabrics are of Swiss manufacture.

tombstone.epitaph: Scrapbook (Switzerland), ca. 1900; silk; Closed book: 31 x 25.5 x 6.5 cm (12 3/16 x 10 1/16 x 2 9/16 in. ); 1967-54-3
